steps.instruction:
### Prep
- Cut one half of red pepper into bite size pieces (2/3 cup)
- Coarsely chop the cilantro
- Cut Pork lengthwise, turn and slice evenly into thin strips


### Steps
1. Place peppers, 2/3 cup of the cilantro, 1/2 cup of onions, 1/4 cup of oil, paprika, cumin, garlic, tomato paste, water and crushed red pepper into blender
2. Blend until smooth 
3. Preheat of large sauté on medium-high for 2 to 3 minutes
4. Coat bread with cooking spray
5. Cook for 1 minute on each side
6. Preheat saute pan on medium high heat for 2 to 3 minutes
7. Season pork wit salt and pepper
8. Place 1 table of oil into the pan 
9. Put the pork onto the pan
10. Cook for 3 to 4 minutes
11. Reduce heat to low
12. Add sauce
13. Cook for 1 to 2 minutes
14. Top each flatbread with pork mixture 
15. Stir 1/4 cup of onions into the yogurt
16. Spoon the yogurt on top of the pork flat bread 
17 Sprinkle with 1/3 cup of cilantro
